  "description": "A dramatic scene of a large wave breaking near a coastal cliff and observation point. The wave is curling powerfully, creating white foam as it crashes down. A small building with an American flag is perched on the cliff overlooking the ocean. Several people are visible both on the observation platform and walking along the cliffside pathway. The coastline is rocky and the landscape is a mix of brown earth, green vegetation, and blue ocean. The sky is clear and bright.",
